112
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:20,959
[SPEAKER_03] Unutra.

113
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:21,439
[SPEAKER_03] Unutra.

114
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:21,759
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

115
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:27,759
[SPEAKER_01] Imali su pripravnike u toj ekipi.

116
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:29,759
[SPEAKER_03] Definitivno sam bio jedini pripravnik.

117
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

118
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:30,399
