121
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da ste me možda imali.

122
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:38,480
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je neriješen.

123
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,079
[SPEAKER_03] To je neriješen.

124
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:40,800
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

125
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,839
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, dobio sam izlaganje.

126
00:07:42,079 --> 00:07:46,240
[SPEAKER_03] Cisco je zanimljiv za sve koji ne znaju jer morate voziti između sastanaka, zar ne?

127
00:07:46,319 --> 00:07:46,879
